('1', 'TIK1205', 'Bahasa Inggris 1', 1, 2015, 2, 1, 2, 0, 'Setelah mengikuti mata kuliah ini, mahasiswa diharapkan dapat: Mengidentifikasi bentuk tunggal dan jamak dari kata benda,\r\nMengidentifikasi struktur, tujuan dan karakteristik dari teks deskriptif , Mengidentifikasi kata sifat, Mendeskripsikan benda (elemen\r\ndasar computer) dengan benar (menulis teks deskripsi), Mengidentifikasi struktur, tujuan, dan karakteristik teks prosedur,\r\nMenjelaskan cara mengoperasikan benda (menulis teks prosedur).', 'Singular and plural form of noun (computer elements), Identifying the generic structure, objective, and language features of\r\ndescriptive text, present tense, Adjective phrase, Writing a descriptive text, Identifying the generic structure, objective, and language\r\nfeatures of procedure text, The use of connectives dan Writing procedure text', '<ol><li> Azar, Betty Schrampfer. 1992. Fundamentals of English Grammar, Second Edition. New Jersey: Prentice Hall Regents.</li><li>Englishindo. 2015. Descriptive Text: Materi dan Contoh Terlengkap. (http://www.englishindo.com/2015/07/contoh-descriptivetext.html), accessed on February 18th, 2016)</li><li>Englishindo. 2014. ProcedureText: Materi dan Contoh Terlengkap. (http://www.englishindo.com/2014/04/procedure-text.html),\r\naccessed on February 18th, 2016.</li><li>Esteras, Santiago Remacha. 2007. Professional English in Use: for Computer and Internet. Cambridge: Cambridge University\r\nPress</li><li>Esteras, Santiago Remacha. 2007. Infotech English for Computer Users: Fourth Edition. Cambridge: Cambridge University\r\nPress</li><li>Walker, Tricia. 1989. English for Academic Purposes Series Computer science. England: Cassel</li></ol>', '2022-03-25 13:40:38', '2022-03-25 06:40:38'),
('10', 'TIK2207', 'Bahasa Inggris 2', 2, 2015, 2, 1, 2, 0, '<p>Setelah mengikuti mata kuliah ini, mahasiswa diharapkan dapat: Memahami bacaan berupa teks deskripsi, Menuliskan\r\npengalaman tentang penggunaan computer dalam bahasa inggris, Menggunakan ungkapan-ungkapan meminta, menawarkan, dan\r\nmemberi bantuan serta meminta dan member informasi , Menggunakan kata kerja bentuk lampau dalam penulisan recount text ,\r\nMengungkapkan pendapat terkait tema sederhana dalam bahasa inggris, Menggunakan Adverbial clauses dalam kalimat ,\r\nMenggunakan Prepositions yang tepat dalam kaliamat&nbsp;<br></p>', '<p>Reading comprehension: function and features in a computer system, Writing recount text: an experience with computer, Past\r\ntense, Adverbial clauses, Prepositions, Expressions of asking, offering, and giving a help, Expressions of asking and giving\r\ninformation, Giving opinion about computer application in everyday life<br></p>', '<ol><li>Azar, Betty Schrampfer. 1992. Fundamentals of English Grammar, Second Edition. New Jersey: Prentice Hall Regents.</li><li>Englishindo. 2015. Descriptive Text: Materi dan Contoh Terlengkap. (http://www.englishindo.com/2015/07/contoh-descriptivetext.html), accessed on February 18th, 2016)</li><li>Englishindo. 2014. ProcedureText: Materi dan Contoh Terlengkap. (http://www.englishindo.com/2014/04/procedure-text.html),\r\naccessed on February 18th, 2016.</li><li>Esteras, Santiago Remacha. 2007. Professional English in Use: for Computer and Internet. Cambridge: Cambridge University\r\nPress</li><li>Esteras, Santiago Remacha. 2007. Infotech English for Computer Users: Fourth Edition. Cambridge: Cambridge University\r\nPress\r\n6. Walker, Tricia. 1989. English for Academic Purposes Series Computer science. England: Cassel</li></ol>', '2022-03-25 14:17:02', '2022-03-25 07:17:02'),
