('112', 'IFK-2322', 'Pemrograman Berorientasi Objek', 2, 2022, 3, 3, 1, 2, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\">Kuliah ini mengajarkan konsep pemrograman berorientasi obyek disertai contoh penerapan konsep pemrograman berorientasi</span><br style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\">obyek pada bahasa pemrograman. Pada kuliah ini mahasiswa diharapkan dapat merancang dan mengimplementasikan</span><br style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\">permasalahan ke dalam kons