('131', 'IFK-4339', 'Sistem Informasi Geografis', 4, 2022, 3, 3, 1, 2, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\">Mahasiswa memiliki kemampuan memahami konsep SIG, menganalisis data spasial dan merepresentasikan data spasial serta</span><br style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\">mampu mengembangkan Web SIG dalam studi kasus tertentu.</span><br></p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Teori :<br></span></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><li>Konsep Dasar