t;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Praktikum :&nbsp;<br></span></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify;\"><li>Data Cleansing</li><li>Data Processing</li></ol>', '<div class=\"form-group row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Muli, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-9\" style=\"width: 566.273px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; -webkit-box-flex: 0;\"><label class=\"form-label\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><ol style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><li>Efori Buulolo, S.Kom., M.Kom (Data Mining untuk PT)</li><li>Kusrini, Emha Taufiq Luthfi (Algoritma Data Mining)</li><li>Miftahun Huda, M.Kom (Algoritma Data Mining Anlisis data dengan Komputer</li></ol></label></div></div>', '2022-03-26 19:11:03', '2022-03-26 19:11:03'),
